  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research contexts to predict hemolysis in centrifugal blood pumps. The CFD hemolysis model for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump was developed and exercised under ventricular assist device operating conditions. Thirteen credibility factors were reviewed; seven were assessed and six were scoped as not-applicable under the minimal-profile submission. All assessed factors achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels under the reduced-rigor minimal-profile pathway. The model is considered adequate for the purpose described in the accompanying decision record. No structured Context of Use object is provided under the ProfileMinimal conformance declaration.",
