      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions or equivalent benchmark confirms second-order spatial accuracy.",
      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation applied to three systematically refined meshes confirms second-order convergence of velocity and pressure fields in the pump volute region."
    },
    {
